data.description:
This home is a must see! Located in the Pine Lakes Subdivision of Palm Coast, the home provides an extremely desirable location, just minutes away from anything you could possibly need.  Pine Lakes Golf Course is just up the road, and offers several amenities that include; Golfing, a pool, and host of events. There is a new advent hospital just around the corner, a selection of popular restaurants nearby, incredible shopping and entertainment opportunities, and just minutes away from pristine beaches! Don't feel like leaving the house? Stay home and enjoy your own inground pool in your fully fenced, private backyard. The covered lanai is the perfect place to entertain year round or sit and relax with your morning coffee. The master bath has a jacuzzi tub to soak at the end of a long day, and a generous walk-in closet for plenty of shoes! All matching KitchenAid appliances, central vacuum, a 2 car garage, outdoor storage closet, and more!
All information deemed reliable, cannot be guaranteed. Buyer & Agent to Verify.
